plot: When the U.S.S. Fruiterprise is attacked by alien broccoli, Captain Orange is forced to crash-land on the sickly-sweet planet of Marshmalia. But the Marshmalians are under the tyrannical rule of Big Rock Candy Monster, and it'll take Captain Orange and his enterprising crew to cook up a plan to save the pacifist creme-puffs.—Jennifer Skelly
